'''''Between Rounds''''' is an 1899 painting by American artist [[Thomas Eakins]], Goodrich #312. It is part of the collection of the [[Philadelphia Museum of Art]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.philamuseum.org/collections/permanent/42496.html|title=Philadelphia Museum of Art - Collections Object: ''Between Rounds''|first=|last=Philadelphia Museum of Art|publisher=}}</ref>
